const faqs = [
  { q: "Is laser hair removal painful?", a: "Thanks to Falcon 4 Pro's -10°C sapphire cooling system, the process is nearly painless. A slight heat sensation may occur in sensitive areas." },
  { q: "How many sessions are needed?", a: "Average 6-8 sessions. 95%+ hair reduction is targeted. Skin type, hair thickness and hormones affect session count." },
  { q: "I have a tan, can I do it in summer?", a: "Yes. Since Nd:YAG 1064nm wavelength doesn't target melanocytes, it is safely applied on tanned and dark skin." },
  { q: "How long between sessions?", a: "Face & Neck: 4-6 weeks. Body: 6-8 weeks. Planned according to hair cycle (anagen phase)." },
  { q: "What are the side effects?", a: "Temporary redness, slight swelling disappears in 1-2 hours. Burn and spot risk minimized with Falcon 4 Pro." },
  { q: "Can men do it too?", a: "Yes. Applied for men in areas like back, chest, neck, inside nose. We have separate waiting areas." },
  { q: "When after pregnancy/birth?", a: "Not applied during pregnancy. Can start 3-6 months after birth with doctor approval. Safe during breastfeeding." },
  { q: "How to book an appointment?", a: "Via website, WhatsApp or phone. You can choose Şişli or Halkalı branch." },
  { q: "How is pricing?", a: "Varies by area and package. First consultation and skin analysis is free. Per session is cheaper with packages." },
