                    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3008.65!2d28.79!3d41.05!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14caa5df9db6a8eb%3A0xb895e35088c1b864!2sMr.%20Falcon%20Beauty%20Halkal%C4%B1!5e0!3m2!1str!2str!4v1781863289752"
